public final class VolumeSaleInfo
extends com.google.api.client.json.GenericJson

Model definition for Books.VolumeSaleInfo. Any information about a volume related to the eBookstore and/or purchaseability. This information can depend on the country where the request originates from (i.e. books may not be for sale in certain countries). This class models an object which will be transmitted to or from the Books service. To reduce the data transferred during service requests, you may remove members that contain data elements that your application does not need. For a detailed explanation, see: http://code.google.com/p/google-api-java-client/wiki/Json
